entries.title: Thousands of officers prepare to guard Peru capital
entries.description: Almost 12,000 police officers are preparing to guard the Peruvian capital Lima as the country braces for massive protests on Thursday.

entries.title: Taco Bell is bringing back a fan-favorite menu item
entries.description: Taco Bell is bringing back a fan-favorite menu item, but you have to act fast.

entries.title: Backlash follows finding that soccer manager who used 'offensive, racist and Islamophobic' language is 'not a conscious racist'
entries.description: Anti-racism groups and England's Football Association (FA) are denouncing an independent panel's finding that a British soccer manager who used "offensive, racist and Islamophobic" language is "not a conscious racist."

entries.title: Bud Light and Budweiser are getting a makeovers at this year's Super Bowl
entries.description: Anheuser-Busch may no longer be the only alcohol brand to advertise at the Super Bowl, but it will still have a major presence — even as rivals pounce on the opportunity, following a 33-year drought.
